lead_paragraph: Matt Carpenter and Stephen Piscotty hit two-run homers in the fourth, Carlos Martinez pitched seven solid innings and the St. Louis Cardinals beat the Milwaukee Brewers 4-3 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Carpenter and Piscotty Homer to Power Cardinals Over Brewers
